{
  "stem": "142.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How can I-- there was a-- a Polish guy there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then I say, where is God?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he says, God?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This who God goes with.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You have to be very strong to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to myself, the only thing I can do-- that's why I don't remember a lot of things-- I said to myself, I am a robot.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I did just this to my mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, from now on, close your eyes and do whatever needs to be done without asking too much.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is-- this is how I-- we went at least for the first few months.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I didn't know what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I couldn't survive by thinking every time that transport were coming, or where that Moll was coming, you know, with a moter- motorcycle at 2:00 in the morning, you know, and seeing this guy-- this guy, Moll, coming in and selecting the most beautiful girls.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he was a good marksman and-- and just marks-- marks them in the more sensitive places of their body, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And seeing in front of you who dies and-- how can you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is-- there is no comparison about humanity at that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What-- there is no such a thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Can you just clarify for us a little bit who this man Moll was?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Explain to us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- that Moll-- that was a-- a guy that-- he was always-- his left eye was up and down, you know, closing and then opening up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was the guy that was in charge of the crematoriums on the transports.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of-- he will come first.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- mostly, he will come about 1:00, 2:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
